---
// 戦略的コンパクト化 — 手動コンパクトの推奨タイミング
---

<figure class="compact" aria-label="手動コンパクトの推奨タイミング">
  <div class="compact__inner">
    <span class="compact__title-label">手動コンパクトのタイミング</span>

    <div class="compact__config">
      <span class="compact__config-key">autoCompact: false</span>
      <span class="compact__config-note">を設定し、手動でコンパクトを行う</span>
    </div>

    <ol class="compact__list">
      <li class="compact__item">
        <span class="compact__num">01</span>
        <div class="compact__body">
          <strong>探索フェーズ終了後</strong>
          <span>大量の調査内容を圧縮</span>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="compact__item">
        <span class="compact__num">02</span>
        <div class="compact__body">
          <strong>マイルストーン完了後</strong>
          <span>次フェーズに向けてリセット</span>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="compact__item">
        <span class="compact__num">03</span>
        <div class="compact__body">
          <strong>エラー解決後</strong>
          <span>デバッグの試行錯誤を捨てる</span>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="compact__item compact__item--accent">
        <span class="compact__num">04</span>
        <div class="compact__body">
          <strong>使用率 60% を超えたら</strong>
          <span>新しいセッションを開始する</span>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </div>
  <figcaption class="compact__caption">
    <code>/context</code> で現在のトークン使用率を確認できる。
  </figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .compact {
    margin-block: 2.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(
      160deg,
      color-mix(in oklch, var(--surface) 80%, white),
      var(--surface)
    );
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .compact__inner {
    padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.1rem;
  }

  .compact__title-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.67rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .compact__config {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding: 0.65rem 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .compact__config-key {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .compact__config-note {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .compact__list {
    list-style: none !important;
    padding: 0 !important;
    margin: 0 !important;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--bg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .compact__item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2.4rem 1fr;
    align-items: start;
    border-block-end: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 0 !important;

    &:last-child {
      border-block-end: none;
    }
  }

  .compact__item--accent {
    background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent-wash) 50%, var(--bg));
  }

  .compact__num {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    padding-inline: 1.1rem 0;
    padding-block: 0.65rem 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .compact__body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.1rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.1rem 0.6rem 0;

    & strong {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--text);
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    & span {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
  }

  .compact__caption {
    padding: 0.55rem 1.5rem 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    border-block-start: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;

    & code {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      font-style: normal;
      color: var(--accent-deep);
      background: color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent-wash) 60%, var(--bg));
      padding: 0.05rem 0.35rem;
      border-radius: 3px;
      border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklch, var(--accent) 20%, transparent);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .compact__inner {
      padding: 1.25rem 1rem 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
